    "description": "<strong>OMI MOMI</strong> is a simple yet challenging puzzle game.<br>It is the perfect blend of classic 8-bit and 16-bit mechanics, making it a must-play for gamers who appreciate a retro feel.<br><br> The gameplay mechanics are straightforward, but if you enjoy challenging your brain and stimulating your neurons,<br> this puzzle game is perfect for you. <br><br>So are you ready to embark on a puzzle adventure of your life and help Omi and Momi discover what's inside the black hole?<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>• 3 Unique worlds with distinct environments and puzzles to solve<br><br>• A total of 60 levels with varying degrees of difficulty<br><br>• Secret biomes to uncover for the most dedicated players<br><br>• Each character, from the protagonists to the subtle background elements, is lovingly hand-animated with pixel art<br><br>• Easy to pick up gameplay, but difficult to master, making you think a lot while playing Omi Momi<br><br>• Discover a detailed world with pixel art and collect as many gold coins as you can",
